      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and grate<strong> half</strong> your <strong>red</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>remaining red onion</strong> and set aside for later</p>",
