    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>lamb mince</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and <strong>grated onion</strong></p><p>Add 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (save the rest for later!) and mix thoroughly until fully combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p>",
