    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and finely shred</p><p>Slice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!) with your<strong> mayo</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
