    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lamb is cooked, remove it from the oven and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Transfer the<strong> cooked</strong> <strong>lamb</strong> to a clean board and slice into long strips – this is your <strong>lamb doner meat</strong></p>",
